Add some vintage charm to any outfit with these cute little resin rose studs in peachy Salmon.

These studs are set on surgical steel posts with metal backs and are good for any allergy sufferers.

They measure 10mm at the widest point and come in lots of other colours, so please check out my other listings.

name: Black chain link earrings
description:
These earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything!

Made from pewter with a painted finish, they measure 3.6cm long including earring hook. The chain charms measure 2cm diameter.

They come on surgical stainless steel hooks.

name: Antique Brass filigree earrings
description:
These filigree earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything! A really bohemian style earring

They measure 5.8cm long including earring hook and are as light as a feather. The filigree is 4.5cm high x 3.5cm wide.

Available in Antique Brass colour on surgical stainless steel hooks.

name: Oval Filigree earrings
description:
These oval shaped filigree earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything!

They measure 4.8cm long including earring hook and are as light as a feather. The oval filigree is 3.2cm long & 2cm wide.

Available in Gunmetal (dark grey) colour. They come on surgical stainless steel hooks and are nickel & lead free.

name: Snowflake filigree earrings
description:
These snowflake shaped filigree earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything!

They measure 3.6cm long including earring hook and are as light as a feather. The snowflake filigree is 2cm diameter

Available in Silver or Antique Brass colour. Both come on surgical stainless steel hooks and are nickel & lead free.

name: Lacey Hearts gold earrings
description:
These lacey hearts earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything!

They measure 3cm long including earring hook and are as light as a feather. The heart charm is 1.5cm x 1.5cm

Available in Gold (14K plated) colour on surgical stainless steel hooks.

name: Diamond shaped filigree earrings
description:
These little filigree earrings are perfect for day or night and are extremely lightweight and ornately detailed. 

They measure 3.5cm long including earring hook. The diamond filigrees measure 1.5cm x 1.5cm

Available in Gunmetal or Silver on surgical steel hooks.

name: Teardrop shaped filigree earrings
description:
These teardrop shaped filigree earrings are a fantastic everyday or special occasion piece, as they go with everything!

They measure 4.9cm long including earring hook and are as light as a feather. The teardrop filigree is 3.4cm long

Available Gunmetal (dark grey) colour or Silver on surgical stainless steel hooks.
